11 An Act relating to criminal procedure; amending 22
O.S. 2021, Section 340, which relates to procedures
12 for advising grand juries; providing limitations on
the use of grand jury transcripts; establishing
13 notice and hearing procedures for releasing grand
jury transcripts; making hearings closed to the
14 public; providing an exception; providing limitations
on representing certain parties; allowing
15 prosecutions concurrent to civil litigation related
to grand jury transcripts; allowing the disclosure of
16 transcribed testimony to witnesses under certain
circumstances; making witnesses subject to
17 restrictions on disclosure; providing penalties for
violations; and providing an effective date.
